lass=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fca1701664154061.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fca1701664154061.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fca1701664154061.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fca1701664154061\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This section, as defined in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uproperties.ini</code> file, defines one or\n\t\tmore property groups which can be used by property definitions instead of (multiple) lists\n\t\tof individual properties. Each line specifies a single property group. Property groups are\n\t\tused for easy reference, for example when several widgets share the same group of\n\t\tproperties.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fca1701664154061__section_kkj_wqr_qzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d818875e52\">Syntax</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104fca1701664154061_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"fca1701664154061__codeblock_rwn_xqr_qzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[propertygroups]\n<code class=\"ph codeph language-plaintext\"><em class=\"ph i\">PropertyGroupId = PropertyId1{;PropertyId2{...;PropertyIdN}}</em></code></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p\">See the following table for syntax details:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fca1701664154061__table_q55_1rr_qzb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">PropertyGroups syntax description</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Syntax</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">PropertyGroupId</code></em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies the name or id of the property group; note that is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\talways prefixed with <code class=\"ph codeph\">grp:</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><em class=\"ph i\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">PropertyId</code></em></td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Specifies a single property using its\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">PropertyId</code>, including its (optional) prefix, or\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tanother property group.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fca1701664154061__section_grh_drr_qzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d818875e124\">Example:</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104fca1701664154061_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"fca1701664154061__codeblock_lmk_2rr_qzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">grp:ux_field=grp:flex_item;grp:grid_item\ngrp:ux_editable=html:readonly;html:disabled\ngrp:ux_text_common=html:placeholder\ngrp:ux_text=grp:ux_text_common;html:maxlength;html:minlength;html:spellcheck\ngrp:ux_text_field=grp:ux_field;grp:ux_editable;grp:ux_prefix_suffix;grp:ux_change_button;grp:ux_text;html:pattern;html:type;html:size;label-text</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/orx1701663500155.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uproperties.ini</a><p>The uproperties.ini file defines the syntax of properties as well as property groups for web widgets.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5442530\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5442530\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[PropertyGroups] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This section, as defined in the uproperties.ini file, defines one or more property groups which can be used by property definitions instead of (multiple) lists of individual properties. Each line specifies a single property group. Property groups are used for easy reference, for example when several widgets share the same group of properties. Syntax Explain this code [propertygroups] PropertyGroupId = PropertyId1{;PropertyId2{...;PropertyIdN}} Copy See the following table for syntax details: Table 1. PropertyGroups syntax description Syntax Description PropertyGroupId Specifies the name or id of the property group; note that is always prefixed with grp: PropertyId Specifies a single property using its PropertyId , including its (optional) prefix, or another property group. Example: Explain this code grp:ux_field=grp:flex_item;grp:grid_item grp:ux_editable=html:readonly;html:disabled grp:ux_text_common=html:placeholder grp:ux_text=grp:ux_text_common;html:maxlength;html:minlength;html:spellcheck grp:ux_text_field=grp:ux_field;grp:ux_editable;grp:ux_prefix_suffix;grp:ux_change_button;grp:ux_text;html:pattern;html:type;html:size;label-text Copy Related Links uproperties.ini The uproperties.ini file defines the syntax of properties as well as property groups for web widgets. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}